### 공통 변수
@host = http://localhost:8080/api
@pid = 1

### [관리자] 로그인
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@a.com",
  "password": "111111"
}
> {%
    const data = (typeof response.body === 'string') ? JSON.parse(response.body) : response.body;
    client.global.set("adminToken", data.accessToken);
%}

### [관리자] 임의의 프로젝트 ID (수동 지정 또는 /projects 조회)
@pid_admin = 1

### [관리자] 목록 (200)
GET {{host}}/projects/{{pid_admin}}/feedback?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [관리자] 작성 (201)
POST {{host}}/projects/{{pid_admin}}/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "content": "관리자 코멘트" }
> {%
    const data = (typeof response.body === 'string') ? JSON.parse(response.body) : response.body;
    client.global.set("fbId_admin", String(data.id));
%}

### [관리자] 수정 (200)
PATCH {{host}}/projects/{{pid_admin}}/feedback/{{fbId_admin}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "content": "관리자 코멘트(수정)" }

### [관리자] 삭제 (204)
DELETE {{host}}/projects/{{pid_admin}}/feedback/{{fbId_admin}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
